It also links to the [http://meta.wikimedia.org/wiki/Help:Contents MediaWiki User's Guide] that contains information about how our wiki software works.

Should you have any questions ''related to the Wiki'', you can always join our IRC channel [irc://irc.gentoo.org/gentoo-wiki #gentoo-wiki on irc.gentoo.org] or email us at [mailto:wiki@gentoo.org wiki@gentoo.org]. ('''Note:''' We do not provide general Gentoo support!)
